#: src/platforms/wasm.md:45
msgid ""
"**Threading**: `perry/thread` `parallelMap`/`parallelFilter`/`spawn` via Web "
"Worker pool with one WASM instance per worker (see "
"[Threading](../threading/overview.md))"
msgstr ""

#: src/platforms/wasm.md:46
